83
00:06:52,750 --> 00:06:53,390
What?

84
00:06:54,190 --> 00:06:55,270
In the hospital?

85
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,120
We've just been out of touch
for a few days.

86
00:06:57,310 --> 00:06:58,830
Things escalated quickly, huh?

87
00:06:59,190 --> 00:07:00,680
I told you it's not.

88
00:07:01,630 --> 00:07:02,680
I better hang up now.

89
00:07:04,070 --> 00:07:05,000
(Wait, you are...)

90
00:07:19,630 --> 00:07:20,870
(You two getting married,)

91
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,160
(I'm totally on board with it.)

92
00:07:22,630 --> 00:07:24,120
(Wish you a lifetime of happiness)

93
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:25,190
