94
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,800
Did I wake you up?

95
00:07:41,270 --> 00:07:42,040
No.

96
00:07:43,270 --> 00:07:44,040
What are you doing?

97
00:07:46,310 --> 00:07:47,800
Chen Fangzhou called you.

98
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:49,800
