99
00:07:50,070 --> 00:07:50,720
He said...

100
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,390
You'll go to see...

101
00:07:53,510 --> 00:07:54,160
Dong.

102
00:07:54,830 --> 00:07:56,120
You go meet up with Dong.

103
00:08:01,950 --> 00:08:03,120
Who's Dong?

104
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,950
He is also my childhood friend,

105
00:08:09,510 --> 00:08:10,480
just like Chen Fangzhou.

106
00:08:11,510 --> 00:08:13,270
They used to know Xu Jingyang.

107
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,830
But then, they forgot.

108
00:08:18,630 --> 00:08:19,600
Just the same as

109
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,510
what you posted?

110
00:08:21,430 --> 00:08:22,720
Xu Jingyang has been wiped

111
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,480
from everyone's memories?

112
00:08:27,190 --> 00:08:27,870
Exactly.

113
00:08:30,270 --> 00:08:31,950
If he isn't a space traveler,

114
00:08:33,750 --> 00:08:34,600
why does everyone

115
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:35,680
seem to have forgotten him?

116
00:08:39,870 --> 00:08:40,830
I don't know.

117
00:08:43,830 --> 00:08:45,120
Could they remember

118
00:08:45,510 --> 00:08:46,120
but pretend not to

119
00:08:46,160 --> 00:08:47,240
in front of you?

120
00:08:50,190 --> 00:08:51,600
Why did they do that?

121
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:53,600
I don't know.

122
00:08:54,430 --> 00:08:55,720
I'm curious about

123
00:08:56,430 --> 00:08:58,160
Xu Jingyang's role

124
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,310
in the experiment

125
00:09:00,070 --> 00:09:01,750
of Lighthouse System.

126
00:09:04,190 --> 00:09:05,190
Only participants can have

127
00:09:05,270 --> 00:09:06,680
that special phone he gave you,

128
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:08,160
which means

129
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:10,310
he might be one of them.

130
00:09:12,040 --> 00:09:12,870
But in the photo

131
00:09:12,870 --> 00:09:13,720
Professor Lu gave you,

132
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:14,430
he clearly looks like

133
00:09:14,430 --> 00:09:16,190
a researcher at Light Laboratory.

134
00:09:18,920 --> 00:09:20,240
Huo Boyu is the same.

135
00:09:21,950 --> 00:09:23,390
He is one of the developers,

136
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:25,800
and a voluntary participant.

137
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:27,870
Are you sure

138
00:09:27,950 --> 00:09:29,070
Xu Jingyang you know

139
00:09:30,310 --> 00:09:32,190
is Noah in the photo?

140
00:09:39,750 --> 00:09:40,750
What do you mean?

141
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:43,630
Show me that photo.

142
00:10:02,160 --> 00:10:04,160
How old was he in 2008?

143
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:07,430
He was...

144
00:10:09,750 --> 00:10:10,670
14 years old.

145
00:10:11,550 --> 00:10:13,480
How could

146
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:16,030
a 14-year-old middle school student

147
00:10:16,030 --> 00:10:17,000
be the same person

148
00:10:17,270 --> 00:10:18,270
as this adult?

149
00:10:28,630 --> 00:10:30,240
Why does everyone forget

150
00:10:30,670 --> 00:10:32,240
someone who clearly existed?

151
00:10:44,790 --> 00:10:45,390
Lian!

152
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,320
Chen Fangzhou and Xu Jingyang

153
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:47,870
got beaten up by the yellow-haired guy
at the market!

154
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:11,440
Go away.

155
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:01,870
Hao,

156
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:02,790
he is here.

157
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:23,750
Fight!

158
00:12:24,410 --> 00:12:27,050
♪Now every time I can feel the wind♪

159
00:12:27,050 --> 00:12:30,130
♪The whole world draws back as it roars♪

160
00:12:30,710 --> 00:12:33,230
♪No need to tell me what to do♪

161
00:12:33,230 --> 00:12:37,010
♪In this rush, I feel, I see♪

162
00:12:37,050 --> 00:12:39,330
♪Just let me flow♪

163
00:12:39,530 --> 00:12:41,690
♪Feeling the pull of time and space♪

164
00:12:41,820 --> 00:12:44,360
♪Clutching the wind in my grasp♪

165
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:46,380
♪On paths untrodden♪

166
00:12:46,380 --> 00:12:49,050
♪We don't have to wait for the light♪

167
00:12:49,050 --> 00:12:50,680
♪My rhythm♪

168
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:56,200
Qi Lian!

169
00:13:01,030 --> 00:13:02,200
Qi Lian, watch out!

170
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:17,030
Xu Jingyang!

171
00:13:28,960 --> 00:13:30,360
Xu Jingyang, he...

172
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:34,870
How about meeting up with your friends?

173
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:36,080
I bet

174
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,150
they must know something.

175
00:13:47,270 --> 00:13:48,120
What about you?

176
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:50,030
Me?

177
00:13:55,270 --> 00:13:56,480
You know that

178
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:59,240
this is your world.

179
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:01,360
You can't go back

180
00:14:01,360 --> 00:14:02,510
to that fantasy world.

181
00:14:03,870 --> 00:14:05,240
What are you going to do?

182
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:11,000
I always tried hard

183
00:14:11,030 --> 00:14:12,270
to change my fate.

184
00:14:13,390 --> 00:14:15,120
But in the end, I ended up with nothing.

185
00:14:16,630 --> 00:14:17,720
I don't want to do that anymore.

186
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:22,630
No matter what comes my way,

187
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:24,790
I want to face it bravely

188
00:14:24,870 --> 00:14:26,000
and cherish what matters.

189
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,240
Everything will be fine.

190
00:14:37,750 --> 00:14:38,910
I'll face it with you.

191
00:15:27,120 --> 00:15:27,750
Qi Lian!

192
00:15:29,510 --> 00:15:30,200
Why didn't you

193
00:15:30,270 --> 00:15:31,000
bring Xiaoyuan here?

194
00:15:32,910 --> 00:15:33,510
Well,

195
00:15:34,840 --> 00:15:36,150
it's been a while since we gathered.

196
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:37,360
Having her wouldn't hurt.

197
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:39,080
Or you didn't tell her?

198
00:15:39,750 --> 00:15:40,440
Say something.

199
00:15:40,630 --> 00:15:41,480
Did you tell her?

200
00:15:44,750 --> 00:15:45,510
You had this hairstyle

201
00:15:45,720 --> 00:15:46,790
six years ago.

202
00:15:47,750 --> 00:15:48,390
Where are you going?

203
00:15:48,550 --> 00:15:49,240
Right here.

204
00:15:49,630 --> 00:15:50,390
Too crowded inside.

205
00:15:50,630 --> 00:15:51,750
It's more spacious out here.

206
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:57,670
Lian.

207
00:15:58,080 --> 00:15:58,670
Lian.

208
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:00,120
Lian.

209
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:06,030
Sit.

210
00:16:06,510 --> 00:16:07,200
Take your seat.

211
00:16:07,910 --> 00:16:09,360
Sit.

212
00:16:14,150 --> 00:16:14,910
Lian,

213
00:16:15,960 --> 00:16:17,030
it's been years.

214
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:19,790
We knew you were busy,

215
00:16:20,030 --> 00:16:21,670
so we didn't want to bother you.

216
00:16:21,790 --> 00:16:22,790
Yes, Lian.

217
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:23,790
Qi Lian is here.

218
00:16:23,960 --> 00:16:25,120
The dust has settled.

219
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:26,360
The past is all behind us now.

220
00:16:27,080 --> 00:16:28,840
Everyone is doing well these years.

221
00:16:29,550 --> 00:16:31,000
Dong's running a business

222
00:16:31,080 --> 00:16:32,200
and got married.

223
00:16:33,270 --> 00:16:34,510
Yong opened a courier station.

224
00:16:34,750 --> 00:16:35,840
He's quite a busy man now.

225
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:38,030
San works on a construction site.

226
00:16:38,670 --> 00:16:39,960
He is a subcontractor,

227
00:16:40,030 --> 00:16:41,120
throwing his weight around.

228
00:16:41,200 --> 00:16:42,320
He's quite the character.

229
00:16:42,720 --> 00:16:43,720
Don't joke around.

230
00:16:44,030 --> 00:16:45,000
I got a family to support.

231
00:16:45,600 --> 00:16:46,720
Aren't you doing great yourself,

232
00:16:47,150 --> 00:16:48,320
managing such a big hair salon?

233
00:16:49,790 --> 00:16:51,360
I owe a lot to Mr. Qi for helping out,

234
00:16:51,870 --> 00:16:52,600
both with money and energy.

235
00:16:52,870 --> 00:16:54,510
He helped me set up the salon.

236
00:16:55,480 --> 00:16:56,080
That's right.

237
00:16:56,510 --> 00:16:57,240
Lian also lent a hand

238
00:16:57,390 --> 00:16:58,750
with my courier station.

239
00:16:59,270 --> 00:17:00,790
Lian also helped me...

240
00:17:02,390 --> 00:17:03,320
Lian chipped in

241
00:17:04,120 --> 00:17:05,960
for the startup money for my business.

242
00:17:06,630 --> 00:17:07,510
That taxi...

243
00:17:08,440 --> 00:17:09,670
Lian bought it for me.

244
00:17:12,870 --> 00:17:13,270
That's fine.

245
00:17:13,790 --> 00:17:14,510
We are close friends.

246
00:17:14,670 --> 00:17:16,120
Don't make it awkward

247
00:17:16,390 --> 00:17:17,910
and keep the gratitude in our hearts.

248
00:17:18,030 --> 00:17:18,510
Raise your glasses,

249
00:17:20,150 --> 00:17:20,960
to Lian.

250
00:17:22,240 --> 00:17:22,550
Yes.

251
00:17:22,750 --> 00:17:23,120
To Lian.

252
00:17:23,240 --> 00:17:23,550
Right,

253
00:17:23,550 --> 00:17:23,790
to Lian.

254
00:17:23,870 --> 00:17:24,720
To Lian.

255
00:17:26,480 --> 00:17:27,150
Qi Lian?

256
00:17:40,790 --> 00:17:41,550
Let me fill it up for you.

257
00:17:49,840 --> 00:17:50,720
No, thanks.

258
00:17:51,240 --> 00:17:52,600
I've been set up.

259
00:17:53,240 --> 00:17:54,150
