smoking and drinking.

260
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:56,030
You are not in a relationship yet.

261
00:17:56,150 --> 00:17:57,390
Already got... some rules?

262
00:17:57,390 --> 00:17:57,870
Stop that.

263
00:17:59,150 --> 00:18:00,080
I'll replace alcohol with tea.

264
00:18:00,240 --> 00:18:01,270
Here we go.

265
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:14,510
Qi Lian,

266
00:18:15,840 --> 00:18:16,480
over all these years,

267
00:18:16,550 --> 00:18:17,600
that's in the past.

268
00:18:18,670 --> 00:18:19,790
You've done what you could,

269
00:18:20,600 --> 00:18:21,390
and you gave it your best shot.

270
00:18:22,720 --> 00:18:23,630
I do think

271
00:18:24,840 --> 00:18:26,240
you should let it go.

272
00:18:50,200 --> 00:18:51,750
I've got good news.

273
00:18:54,240 --> 00:18:55,550
I found Xu Jingyang.

274
00:19:26,720 --> 00:19:29,000
But he's not the real Xu Jingyang.

275
00:19:57,000 --> 00:19:58,880
Have you all been
hiding something from me?

276
00:20:17,440 --> 00:20:18,350
I just want to know

277
00:20:18,350 --> 00:20:19,880
if there any wrong with my mind

278
00:20:19,920 --> 00:20:20,960
or if there's something

279
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:21,960
you're not telling me!

280
00:20:33,070 --> 00:20:35,200
Close friends?

281
00:20:35,200 --> 00:20:36,110
That's it, huh?

282
00:20:39,790 --> 00:20:40,160
Lian!

283
00:20:40,350 --> 00:20:40,720
Alright.

284
00:20:40,830 --> 00:20:41,590
Lian!

285
00:20:43,270 --> 00:20:44,160
After this drink,

286
00:20:45,310 --> 00:20:46,310
we'll be strangers.

287
00:20:46,750 --> 00:20:47,400
Lian!

288
00:20:47,590 --> 00:20:48,240
No, Lian!

289
00:20:48,400 --> 00:20:49,270
Lian!

290
00:20:54,110 --> 00:20:55,480
I said we shouldn't hide it.

291
00:20:55,480 --> 00:20:56,720
What about now?

292
00:20:57,550 --> 00:20:58,680
There is indeed such a person.

293
00:21:01,510 --> 00:21:02,790
But he wasn't Xu Jingyang.

294
00:21:03,960 --> 00:21:04,830
His name was Chen Tianyang.

295
00:21:07,880 --> 00:21:08,590
