298
00:21:17,510 --> 00:21:18,440
That day when we fought,

299
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:20,000
the yellow-haired guy

300
00:21:20,070 --> 00:21:21,070
almost pushed you off the second floor.

301
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:21,920
