303
00:21:23,960 --> 00:21:25,480
Then he was sent to the ICU.

304
00:21:35,720 --> 00:21:37,030
And where did he go?

305
00:21:41,000 --> 00:21:41,720
He died.

306
00:22:10,880 --> 00:22:13,030
What are you thinking, Xiaoyuan?

307
00:22:16,790 --> 00:22:17,640
Grandma, have a seat right here..

308
00:22:23,550 --> 00:22:24,480
I was thinking

309
00:22:25,480 --> 00:22:27,000
Grandma's doing much better now,

310
00:22:27,480 --> 00:22:28,720
and I can make money.

311
00:22:29,680 --> 00:22:31,550
Things are looking up
for the days ahead.

312
00:22:33,880 --> 00:22:35,750
When I make more money,

313
00:22:36,030 --> 00:22:37,590
