324
00:23:07,880 --> 00:23:09,030
A famous makeup artist

325
00:23:09,030 --> 00:23:10,270
wants me to join him.

326
00:23:10,750 --> 00:23:11,310
Well,

327
00:23:11,550 --> 00:23:12,480
I really like

328
00:23:12,480 --> 00:23:13,240
this work.

329
00:23:14,160 --> 00:23:16,160
But I'm not sure

330
00:23:16,160 --> 00:23:17,400
whether it's reliable.

331
00:23:18,350 --> 00:23:20,510
This job might not be

332
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:22,880
as steady as

333
00:23:22,920 --> 00:23:23,920
working in the salon.

334
00:23:27,880 --> 00:23:30,000
You're a restless girl.

335
00:23:31,070 --> 00:23:32,440
You're just naturally

336
00:23:32,440 --> 00:23:33,640
not into being steady.

337
00:23:34,310 --> 00:23:35,790
It's not you

338
00:23:35,790 --> 00:23:36,750
if you really like something

339
00:23:36,960 --> 00:23:38,400
but you let it go.

340
00:23:44,160 --> 00:23:44,790
Xiaoyuan,

341
00:23:46,310 --> 00:23:47,240
go ahead and be wilful.

342
00:23:48,880 --> 00:23:50,070
Grandma supports you.

343
00:24:00,400 --> 00:24:01,310
Over these years,

344
00:24:02,920 --> 00:24:05,000
You've suffered a lot

345
00:24:07,310 --> 00:24:09,200
because of my illness.

346
00:24:13,830 --> 00:24:15,880
Grandma has seen it all.

347
00:24:20,480 --> 00:24:21,270
Xiaoyuan,

348
00:24:24,270 --> 00:24:26,070
I'm so sorry.

349
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:29,680
That's okay, Grandma.

350
00:24:30,510 --> 00:24:32,310
We are family.

351
00:24:37,350 --> 00:24:38,310
Sweetie...

352
00:24:46,240 --> 00:24:47,000
From now on,

353
00:24:47,720 --> 00:24:49,550
do whatever

354
00:24:49,750 --> 00:24:50,830
you want to do.

355
00:24:51,400 --> 00:24:52,350
Remember that.

356
00:24:54,000 --> 00:24:55,590
Grandma's always behind you.

357
00:25:00,350 --> 00:25:01,070
My sweetie?

358
00:25:06,480 --> 00:25:07,880
After Yang was taken to the hospital,

359
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:10,160
they tried hard to save him.

360
00:25:11,200 --> 00:25:12,640
But he couldn't make it.

361
00:25:16,440 --> 00:25:17,160
Later,

362
00:25:17,720 --> 00:25:18,400
their family

363
00:25:18,480 --> 00:25:19,790
moved away from Baiyang.

364
00:25:29,920 --> 00:25:31,510
You were depressed for a long time

365
00:25:32,160 --> 00:25:33,790
after knowing about this

366
00:25:34,240 --> 00:25:35,030
You always believed that

367
00:25:35,070 --> 00:25:36,110
it was my fault.

368
00:25:37,270 --> 00:25:38,550
Things got worse,

369
00:25:38,920 --> 00:25:39,880
so your father took you overseas

370
00:25:39,880 --> 00:25:41,070
to see a psychiatrist.

371
00:25:42,270 --> 00:25:43,200
And then,

372
00:25:44,790 --> 00:25:46,310
we didn't stay in touch for many years.

373
00:25:47,240 --> 00:25:48,310
After you returned,

374
00:25:49,750 --> 00:25:50,720
Fatty told us

375
00:25:51,070 --> 00:25:52,590
you had forgotten about Yang

376
00:25:53,880 --> 00:25:55,270
and you constantly searching for someone

377
00:25:55,310 --> 00:25:56,270
named Xu Jingyang.

378
00:25:58,030 --> 00:25:59,030
But Yang's full name

379
00:26:00,070 --> 00:26:01,310
was Chen Tianyang.

380
00:26:03,680 --> 00:26:04,640
So we were thinking,

381
00:26:05,070 --> 00:26:06,160
maybe your psychiatrist

382
00:26:06,270 --> 00:26:07,310
hypnotized you for treatment,

383
00:26:08,110 --> 00:26:09,400
making you forget about all of this.

384
00:26:11,920 --> 00:26:13,240
I insisted that we say

385
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:15,440
that we don't know Xu Jingyang.

386
00:26:16,790 --> 00:26:17,880
Anyway, in your mind,

387
00:26:18,680 --> 00:26:20,270
Xu Jingyang is alive.

388
00:26:21,790 --> 00:26:23,270
It's better to search for
a missing person

389
00:26:24,350 --> 00:26:25,590
than to regret a lifetime

390
00:26:25,830 --> 00:26:27,510
over someone who's gone.

391
00:26:50,440 --> 00:26:52,000
Chen Tianyang...

392
00:26:55,920 --> 00:26:57,830
Do you have his photo?

393
00:27:36,830 --> 00:27:37,790
Hello?

394
00:27:39,240 --> 00:27:40,030
(Are you Jiang Xiaoyuan?)

395
00:27:40,640 --> 00:27:41,510
Yes, and you are...?

396
00:27:41,960 --> 00:27:42,750
(Jiang Xiaoyuan,)

397
00:27:43,920 --> 00:27:44,720
(get yourself organized)

398
00:27:44,750 --> 00:27:46,400
(for the little sober time.)

399
00:27:46,960 --> 00:27:48,720
(Stop digging for any more truths.)

400
00:27:49,590 --> 00:27:50,400
(Or,)

401
00:27:51,070 --> 00:27:51,880
(we will retaliate)

402
00:27:51,920 --> 00:27:53,200
(against you like mad.)

403
00:27:54,070 --> 00:27:55,510
(You go crazy alone,)

404
00:27:56,110 --> 00:27:57,680
(or make everyone around you)

405
00:27:57,680 --> 00:27:58,550
(die together?)

406
00:27:59,070 --> 00:28:00,240
(It's up to you.)

407
00:28:28,590 --> 00:28:29,400
Hello, Qi Lian.

408
00:28:29,830 --> 00:28:30,590
Are you okay?

409
00:28:31,160 --> 00:28:31,790
(Hi, Xiaoyuan.)

410
00:28:33,310 --> 00:28:34,110
Fangzhou?

411
00:28:35,400 --> 00:28:36,160
Is Qi Lian

412
00:28:36,160 --> 00:28:37,000
with you now?

413
00:28:37,270 --> 00:28:38,070
Come over quickly.

414
00:28:38,270 --> 00:28:39,110
He's in trouble now.

415
00:28:43,120 --> 00:28:44,680
[Hou Hot Pot]

416
00:28:44,680 --> 00:28:45,240
Easy.

417
00:28:45,960 --> 00:28:47,240
You didn't drink that much,

418
00:28:47,400 --> 00:28:47,960
