419
00:28:48,000 --> 00:28:48,680
Are you this drunk already?

420
00:28:49,750 --> 00:28:50,350
Take it slow.

421
00:28:50,350 --> 00:28:51,110
Slow down.

422
00:28:52,070 --> 00:28:52,720
If you can't handle it,

423
00:28:52,830 --> 00:28:53,480
just drink less.

424
00:28:53,590 --> 00:28:54,110
Qi Lian!

425
00:28:54,880 --> 00:28:56,030
Qi Lian! What's going on?

426
00:28:56,350 --> 00:28:57,590
Did you call the police?

427
00:28:58,000 --> 00:28:59,720
Xiaoyuan, why are you crying?

428
00:29:00,160 --> 00:29:01,640
Tell me. What's wrong with him?

429
00:29:01,880 --> 00:29:03,310
I didn't expect that to happen.

430
00:29:03,480 --> 00:29:04,160
He... Nothing's wrong with him.

431
00:29:04,270 --> 00:29:05,030
He's just drunk.

432
00:29:05,270 --> 00:29:06,200
I was kidding.

433
00:29:06,400 --> 00:29:07,240
Here, hold him for a second.

434
00:29:07,400 --> 00:29:08,110
I need to use the bathroom.

435
00:29:08,110 --> 00:29:09,550
I... I really have to go.

436
00:29:13,270 --> 00:29:14,480
Mind that step.

437
00:29:20,350 --> 00:29:21,640
Your injury hasn't healed.

438
00:29:21,920 --> 00:29:23,110
Let's get into the car.

439
00:29:23,720 --> 00:29:24,350
Let's go.

440
00:29:32,680 --> 00:29:33,550
Xiaoyuan,

441
00:29:34,350 --> 00:29:35,070
don't go.

442
00:29:36,200 --> 00:29:37,280
Don't leave me.

443
00:29:40,200 --> 00:29:40,960
I'm not leaving.

444
00:29:41,550 --> 00:29:43,110
I'll be here with you.

445
00:29:45,720 --> 00:29:47,200
Thankfully, you're okay.

446
00:30:02,720 --> 00:30:03,830
Actually,

447
00:30:04,790 --> 00:30:07,390
I was so eager to uncover the truth.

448
00:30:10,000 --> 00:30:12,110
But now, I know the truth.

449
00:30:13,280 --> 00:30:14,680
It scares me.

450
00:30:18,480 --> 00:30:20,280
I fear for people around me

451
00:30:20,280 --> 00:30:21,590
will get hurt.

452
00:30:24,040 --> 00:30:25,550
I worry about

453
00:30:26,760 --> 00:30:27,680
what should I do

454
00:30:27,720 --> 00:30:29,110
if one day

455
00:30:30,070 --> 00:30:31,150
I go crazy.

456
00:30:33,000 --> 00:30:35,620
♪If time were to reset♪

457
00:30:35,990 --> 00:30:38,420
♪Would you dare to join me yet?♪

458
00:30:39,860 --> 00:30:42,410
♪At the start of this quest♪

459
00:30:42,970 --> 00:30:45,510
♪Would you wait for me?♪

460
00:30:46,910 --> 00:30:50,580
♪In endless night♪

461
00:30:52,280 --> 00:30:53,590
Why do you sit there?

462
00:30:54,240 --> 00:30:54,920
Xiaoyuan,

463
00:30:55,070 --> 00:30:56,200
Don't sit there.

464
00:30:56,350 --> 00:30:57,150
The ground is cold.

465
00:30:57,790 --> 00:30:58,680
Let's go.

466
00:31:02,070 --> 00:31:03,790
How come he is so heavy?

467
00:31:09,200 --> 00:31:10,070
Careful.

468
00:31:21,680 --> 00:31:22,720
What did you talk about?

469
00:31:23,350 --> 00:31:24,310
He is so drunk now.

470
00:31:25,720 --> 00:31:27,200
Just some past matters.

471
00:31:28,520 --> 00:31:30,150
Something about Xu Jingyang?

472
00:31:31,790 --> 00:31:32,520
You know him?

473
00:31:34,480 --> 00:31:35,550
All those things are in the past.

474
00:31:36,550 --> 00:31:37,590
Just move on, and it'll be okay.

475
00:31:44,390 --> 00:31:45,150
So does Xu Jingyang

476
00:31:45,240 --> 00:31:46,390
really exist?

477
00:31:48,760 --> 00:31:49,310
Xiaoyuan,

478
00:31:50,000 --> 00:31:51,310
you don't have to get into this.

479
00:31:51,590 --> 00:31:53,440
And don't bring it up
in front of Qi Lian.

480
00:31:54,280 --> 00:31:55,870
Yang has gone for many years.

481
00:31:56,390 --> 00:31:57,720
It's time to move on.

482
00:31:58,520 --> 00:31:59,350
Living in the present

483
00:31:59,390 --> 00:32:00,280
is what matters most.

484
00:32:01,630 --> 00:32:02,720
That's Qi Lian exactly.

485
00:32:03,760 --> 00:32:05,630
He'll treat someone he cared about

486
00:32:06,350 --> 00:32:07,480
for the rest of his life.

487
00:32:08,830 --> 00:32:10,070
Still remember back in high school,

488
00:32:10,550 --> 00:32:11,110
we all knew

489
00:32:11,110 --> 00:32:12,070
that he liked you.

490
00:32:12,630 --> 00:32:13,070
But at that time,

491
00:32:13,110 --> 00:32:14,310
