496
00:32:22,040 --> 00:32:23,390
But who knows?

497
00:32:23,720 --> 00:32:25,110
So many years have passed.

498
00:32:27,040 --> 00:32:28,390
All joking aside,

499
00:32:28,960 --> 00:32:29,680
