507
00:32:49,830 --> 00:32:50,590
Think about it.

508
00:32:50,870 --> 00:32:52,040
When you first came to the salon,

509
00:32:52,240 --> 00:32:53,200
you were acting that

510
00:32:53,200 --> 00:32:54,350
