516
00:33:05,520 --> 00:33:07,150
(You go crazy alone,)

517
00:33:07,720 --> 00:33:09,200
(or make everyone around you)

518
00:33:09,310 --> 00:33:10,070
(die together?)

519
00:33:11,630 --> 00:33:12,720
(It's up to you.)

520
00:33:28,000 --> 00:33:29,960
(What a pity for you waiting for me
