521
00:33:32,150 --> 00:33:33,200
(In the end,)

522
00:33:34,790 --> 00:33:35,680
(the one you've been waiting for)

523
00:33:35,680 --> 00:33:37,280
(will end up being crazy.)

524
00:34:17,960 --> 00:34:19,000
Let me help you to get him inside.

525
00:34:19,480 --> 00:34:20,440
No, Fangzhou.

526
00:34:20,870 --> 00:34:21,590
You'd better

527
00:34:21,630 --> 00:34:22,550
