545
00:36:19,590 --> 00:36:20,070
Please make way!

546
00:36:20,230 --> 00:36:21,230
Make way!

547
00:36:22,040 --> 00:36:22,630
Chen Fangzhou?

548
00:36:23,360 --> 00:36:24,230
Hurry!

549
00:36:25,920 --> 00:36:26,480
Give us a hand.

550
00:36:27,880 --> 00:36:28,710
Qi Lian?

551
00:36:32,840 --> 00:36:33,440
Jiang Xiaoyuan!

552
00:36:33,630 --> 00:36:34,400
