566
00:36:54,070 --> 00:36:55,110
(die together?)

567
00:36:55,520 --> 00:36:56,800
(It's up to you.)

568
00:36:58,070 --> 00:36:59,000
(Qi Lian...)

569
00:36:59,670 --> 00:37:00,360
(Jiang Xiaoyuan,)

570
00:37:00,960 --> 00:37:01,670
