00:37:38,040 --> 00:37:38,960
Sweetie, take this.

582
00:37:38,960 --> 00:37:40,040
Eat it on the way.

583
00:37:43,190 --> 00:37:43,920
Grandma,

584
00:37:46,270 --> 00:37:47,520
