585
00:37:47,520 --> 00:37:48,270
OK?

586
00:37:49,270 --> 00:37:49,840
Of course.

587
00:37:50,230 --> 00:37:50,960
I'll call you for sure.

588
00:37:53,270 --> 00:37:53,960
That knitting work

589
00:37:54,000 --> 00:37:56,150
